snippet.title: Why Celebrities Are Furious on Amber Heard
snippet.description:
In today’s video you are going to know the reasons for why celebrities are furious on Amber Heard. Even if you didn't know who Amber Heard was before, you must now. 

Right now, we can say that she is one of the most controversial celebrities. We all know that  Amber Heard and her ex-husband Johnny Depp are at the center of a significant dispute. 

Some celebs have weighed in on Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's complicated relationship. Celebs have taken their sides. Some have shown support for their long-time friend Johnny Depp and some have sided with Amber, while some are simply calling out the hypocrisy of Amber.

 Watch the video till the end to understand the real reasons for this controversy.
